      "num": 2,
      "geez": "እስመ፡ ኀያል፡ ውእቱ፡ በኵሉ፡ ኅቡኣተ፡ ጽድቅ፡ ወዐመፃ፡ ከመ፡ ጽላሎት፡ የኀልፍ፡ ወምቅዋም፡ አልቦ፡ እስመ፡ ቆመ፡ ኅሩይ፡ በቅድመ፡ እግዚአ፡ መናፍስት፡ ወስብሐቲሁ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ ወኀይሉ፡ ለትውልደ፡ ትውልድ።",
      "translation": "For he is mighty in all the secrets of righteousness, And unrighteousness shall disappear as a shadow, And have no continuance; Because the Elect One standeth before the Lord of Spirits, And his glory is for ever and ever, And his might unto all generations.",
